      <title>Stellantis 在巴西和印度雇佣 50,000 欧元工程师以节省成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/stellantis-hires-50-000-engineers-in-brazil-india-to-cut-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着汽车制造商应对低成本竞争和需求放缓，Stellantis NV 已开始在摩洛哥、印度和巴西等国家招聘大部分工程人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/stellantis-hires-50-000-engineers-in-brazil-india-to-cut-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
